<plot>Scarlet just got her period today. Vera just realized she is pregnant. Jane is entering menopause. And Nate is... confused. We follow their stories until their paths converge... in the feminine hygiene aisle of the supermarket. Humorous and sharp, the film provides a much needed look into a part of life normally kept under wraps.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?429339</url></doc>
